# V·∫Ω heatmap c√°c bi·∫øn A ƒë∆∞·ª£c ch·ªçn v·ªõi c√°c bi·∫øn B
plt.figure(figsize=(14, 8))
sns.heatmap(corr_submatrix.loc[good_A_features], cmap="coolwarm", fmt=".2f")
plt.title("T∆∞∆°ng quan gi·ªØa c√°c bi·∫øn A (t·ªët) v√† c√°c bi·∫øn B ƒë√£ ch·ªçn")
